<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Last Updated: June 10, 2026</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy applies to LSDADesigns ("we", "us"), operator of the Etsy shop LSDADesigns.<p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how this application ("App") collects, uses, and protects information obtained through the Pinterest API in connection with the operation and promotion of an Etsy store.</p>

    <h2>Information We Access</h2>
    <p>The App may access Pinterest account information, advertising account information, campaign data, analytics data, and other information authorized by the account owner.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>Information is used solely to create, manage, and optimize Pinterest advertising and content for the associated Etsy store.</p>

    <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>Information obtained through Pinterest is not sold or shared except as required by law.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, contact the owner of this application.</p>
</body>
